precis:
Amendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (SCHEDULE NO. 1026) which
provides for the use of dioctyl sodium sulfosuccinate in edible sausage
casings to facilitate the deshirring of folded sausage casings and reduce
breakage.
